-- Romania Plans to Sell Its Entire 46% Stake in Romtelecom, Mediafax Reports
-- B y   I r i n a   S a v u
-- 2010-11-26T11:30:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-26/romania-plans-to-sell-its-entire-46-stake-in-romtelecom-mediafax-reports.html
Romania plans to sell its 46 percent
stake in Romtelecom SA, the country’s former phone monopoly, to
the majority owner,  Hellenic Telecommunications Organization SA ,
or on the stock exchange, Mediafax reported.  The government has asked Hellenic Telecommunications to
submit an offer for the stake by the end of the year, the news
service said today, citing a statement from the  Communications
Ministry . Ministry officials didn’t respond immediately to calls
from Bloomberg seeking comment.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Irina Savu  in Bucharest at 
 isavu@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez in Prague at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  